This paper is likely to belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category as it deals with video quality assessment. Computer Vision (cs.CV) is also a likely category as it involves analyzing visual cues and distortions. Information Theory (cs.IT) could be relevant as it mentions modeling the Human Visual System. Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) is another possible category as it discusses the user experience of 3D video. Graphics (cs.GR) is also a possible category as it involves the creation and display of 3D content.
